<section id="about" class="section relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Visual -->
      <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center lg:col-span-2" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="orb"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <h2 class="text-neutral mb-6 reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Meet Your<br />Practitioner
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-neutral-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <p>Jill brings a grounded, intentional approach to energy healing from her practice in Newport, Maine. No pretense. No pressure. Just focused, compassionate work designed to meet you exactly where you are.</p>
          <p>She creates a safe, judgment-free space where your energy can recalibrate on its own terms. Every session is shaped around what your body and mind actually need &mdash; not a script. The goal is simple: restore balance so you can move through life with more ease.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .orb {
    width: clamp(200px, 50vw, 320px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 40% 35%, oklch(0.65 0.1 290 / 0.45) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 65% 70%, oklch(0.6 0.08 65 / 0.25) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle, oklch(0.3 0.1 280 / 0.6) 0%, transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(1px);
    animation: breathe 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes breathe {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.85; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.04); opacity: 1; }
  }
</style>
